long_description: alain's city and east (a.c.e.) physiotherapy is a boutique clinic based in bethnal green in london's east end and is only minutes away from the city and shoreditch. the clinic's ethos is patient-centred care, with no emphasis on repeat treatments as its vision is to empower patients to improve self-care and management. physiotherapy practice aims to understand the why's and what's of your presenting complaints through an in-depth history taking following by appropriate testing to then provide the best course of treatment and management using various non-invasive modalities. whether you are a recreational athlete or a professional athlete, or from any walks of life or even more so sedentary individuals, physiotherapy can help. he worked as a performer for various musicals in the west end (lion king, king and i amongst others), tv shows in the uk and abroad for many years. alain's aim and vision is to enable his patients to recover from their ailments and improve their lives at all levels as health and well-being is not solely based only on the physical.
